<chapter id="s4s.about">
 <title>What is &sles4sap;?</title>
 <abstract>
 <para>
  &sles4sapreg; is a bundle of software and services that addresses
  specific needs of SAP users.
 </para>
 </abstract>

 <sect1>
  <title>Overview</title>
  <para>
  Target use cases are:
  </para>
  <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Unix to Linux Migrations and Replatforming
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    SAP Appliances
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    SAP Cloud Deployments
   </para>
  </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

  <para>
  &sles4sap; consists of the following software components and concepts:
  </para>
 
  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
   <para>
    &slsreg;
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Installation Wizard
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    &slereg; &hasi;
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Page Cache Limitation
   </para>
  </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

  <!-- the reference platform for SAP's software development.  In -->
  <!--   various ways, it is optimized for SAP. -->
  
  <!--   &sls; &hasi; is also part of the &sles4sap; platform. -->


  <para>The following services for &sles4sap; are available:</para>
  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     Extended Service Pack Overlap Support
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     Separate Update Channel
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
SUSE Linux Enterprise Server Priority Support for SAP Applications (optional)
  </para>
   </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
 </sect1>

 <sect1>
  <title>Software Components</title>
  <para>
  </para>

  <sect2>
   <title>&sls;</title>

   <para>&sls; is the most interoperable platform for mission-critical
   computing, both physical and virtual.  In the context of SAP, these are the most important features:</para>

   <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      SAP's Development Platform
     </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Certified
     </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Optimized
     </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      SAP's preferred Appliance platform
     </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      SAP priority support
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </itemizedlist>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
   <title>Installation Wizard</title>

   <para>The Installation Wizard offers a guided installation for both,
   the &sls; operating system and the SAP applications.</para>

   <para>Additionally, it is an installation framework for third party
   extension.</para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
   <title>&sle; &hasi;</title>

   <para>
   </para>

   <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
     <para>
Cluster manager
     </para>
    </listitem>
<listitem>
     <para>
Cluster filesystem
     </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
     <para>
SAP resource Agents
     </para>
</listitem>
   </itemizedlist>
  </sect2>

 </sect1>
